net.hudup.core.data.ctx

Interface CTSMultiProfiles

  • All Superinterfaces:
    java.lang.Cloneable, java.io.Serializable, Transfer
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    CTSMemMultiProfiles

    public interface CTSMultiProfiles
extends java.io.Serializable, Cloneable, Transfer
    Every context template represented by ContextTemplate interface owns a profile table and each value represented by ContextValue of template corresponds to a row in this table. Each row in such template profile table is represented by Profile class. A class that implements this interface CTSMultiProfiles contains all profiles of all templates. Note that these templates belong to a context template schema represented ContextTemplateSchema interface.
    Version:
    10.0
    Author:
    Loc Nguyen
